Gordon FLACH, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Joseph FARRELL, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4717 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 06, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The parties' stipulation for dismissal filed May 2, 2019, is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is granted. This appeal is dismissed.
